<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>You're registered for {{programDisplayName}}</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: 'DM Sans', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background: #F8F4EF; color: #2D2D2D; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    .wrapper { max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 40px 24px; }
    .header { border-bottom: 2px solid #D4A017; padding-bottom: 16px; margin-bottom: 32px; }
    .brand { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; color: #1A3C5E; letter-spacing: -0.01em; }
    .tagline { font-size: 11px; color: #5a6e7a; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-top: 4px; }
    h1 { font-size: 28px; font-weight: 300; color: #1A3C5E; margin: 0 0 16px; line-height: 1.2; }
    p { font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.7; color: #2D2D2D; margin: 0 0 16px; }
    .detail-row { background: #f0ebe3; border-radius: 4px; padding: 16px 20px; margin: 24px 0; }
    .detail-label { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 500; color: #5a6e7a; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.15em; }
    .detail-value { font-size: 14px; color: #0d1b2a; margin-top: 2px; }
    .footer { margin-top: 40px; padding-top: 16px; border-top: 1px solid #e0d8cc; font-size: 11px; color: #5a6e7a; }
    a { color: #3d7a8a; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="header">
      <div class="brand">Dnyanpith</div>
      <div class="tagline">Environment changes outcomes.</div>
    </div>

    <h1>You're in.</h1>

    <p>Hi {{name}},</p>
    <p>Your registration for <strong>{{programDisplayName}}</strong>{{#if batchName}} — {{batchName}}{{/if}} is confirmed. Payment received.</p>

    <div class="detail-row">
      <div class="detail-label">Invoice</div>
      <div class="detail-value">{{invoiceNumber}}</div>
    </div>

    <p>The invoice is attached to this email. Keep it for your records.</p>

    <p>We'll be in touch with batch details closer to the date. If you have any questions before then, reply to this email or reach out on WhatsApp.</p>

    <p>Looking forward to seeing you.<br />— Arjun, Dnyanpith</p>

    <div class="footer">
      Dnyanpith Abhyasika Pvt. Ltd. · Ambajogai, Maharashtra<br />
      <a href="mailto:hello@dnyanpith.org">hello@dnyanpith.org</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
